image_analysis.description: A scanned image of a financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, Part 6, for Donald J. Trump. The form details various assets and the income derived from them in a tabular format.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with form information and the filer's name. The main body consists of a table with six columns: '#', 'Description', 'EIF', 'Value', 'Income Type', and 'Income Amount'. A footer at the bottom provides the date of the reported information and a document identifier.
